2003-01-23  Dmitriy Anisimkov <anisimkov@yahoo.com>

	* aws-net-std-gnat.adb:
	Changes regarding the AWS.Net API modification.
	(Bind): Rollback empty host to "localhost" substitution.
	 becouse empty host mean all extenal accessible IP addresses
	 of the host, but "localhost" mean IP address for access to the
	 host just locally.
	(Shutdown): internal catch only Socket_Error exception, we should not
	 suppress unexpected errors.
	(Receive): Fix possible dead loop in the Receive procedure when the
	 connection closed by peer.

	* aws-net-std-adasockets.adb:
	Changes regarding the AWS.Net API modification.

2003-01-22  Pascal Obry  <p.obry@wanadoo.fr>

	* makefile:
	(UNITS): New variable used to rebuild all units.
	(check_oslib): New target.
	(build): Do not use a loop for the build process. It depends on
	 UNITS and units are built by this rule. Now the build process
	 stop at the first error. Cleaner build process.

